      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLDEN TUNES (3) has been racing consistently without much luck and wasn't far away when finishing fifth at Balaklava over 1050m last start. He has since changed stables, and he looks well placed in this. On top. BUADES (4) has 2 wins from 19 starts but continues to race honestly, with 5 placings to his name. This looks a suitable assignment and he should be right in the finish again. BON'S A LAD (1) comes here off a determined last-start victory at this track and, from the inside draw, is expected to settle on the speed once more. He appeals as the value runner capable of giving a bold sight. REVOLUTION RISING (2) has been competitive all season despite not having much go his way. He is capable of featuring in the top 4 again with even luck in the running. KURIMUZON (6) has claims on best form and is worth including in the wider exotics.",
